caption.p: Gas chromatogram profiles of peak retention of components of the lemongrass essential oil: 6-methylhept-5-en-2-one (1), camphene (2), limonene (3), nonan-4-ol (4), citronellal (5), citronellol (6), neral (7), geranial (8), citral (9), geranyl acetate (10), β-caryophyllene (11), γ-muurolene (12), and caryophyllene oxide (13).
